Package: liaendmembers
Type: Package
Title: Lead Isotope Provenance Methods
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Karan", "Desai",
      email = "workforce.karan@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: This package integrates advanced lead isotope provenance methods into a unified framework to streamline research workflows. The package employs Principal Component Analysis (PCA) to distinguish isotopic endmembers. It further provides tools for Euclidean distance functions and mass fractionation corrections. Additionally, the system incorporates XGBoost predictive modeling based on user-trained reference datasets.
